messages: b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:25): May I ask your name stranger?
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:25): So, have you had a good day Leasha?
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:26): haha..not a really good month though...haha
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:26): and my youngest girl started preschool today
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:26): what has happened this month?
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:27): haha..well...2 weeks ago we had exams at college
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:27): and my friend and I made a bet
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:28): so, who went worse in the exams, would have to do whatever the other wanted..haha
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:28): so....what have they made you do?
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:29): well..i thought she would ask something like, clean her apartment or carry her bag for a whole week
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:29): but she asked me to shave my head :S
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:30): well..i had to...it was a bet...
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:30): Do you have a before and after photo?
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:32): this pic was from the trip we made.....the bet was created there...hehe
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:32): you had nice long hair :(
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:34): I promise I won't laugh
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:36): Well thats not too bad
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:36): Internet is slow down this end of the world
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:36): the bigger problem is the mocking
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:37): Had you ever had short hair?
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:37): after she shaved my head, she keptthe hair as a souvenir....so sometimes she uses it to mock me
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:37): I don't think your "friend" is very friendly
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:38): hhahah...no, shes just wierd soemtimes...but shes a nice person most of time
9a5e2c7f72ba32f6e8cd8fb80c831f0a (06:38): even being a nice person who cut all of my hair...hahaha
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:39): Well...so long as you are OK with her
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:39): Well, I have to go now....sorry.
b73c7d0d6259b477be957a59146a3e52 (06:40): If you hair is anything like mine it will only be a year or so until it is long again ;)
